					get the oldest time stamp from the possible collection of WODs
					if these WO are created on the web portal for Pelindo1 there will be only one wod

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
25 June 2018	jlgab1	Initial creation

*/

vars
	msd : CM_WodMarineServiceDetail;
